13 following, the Minority Leader of the House, the Minority Leader of the Senate; 3 members
14 appointed by mutual agreement of the Speaker of the House, the Senate President, and the
15 Governor who serve in a leadership capacity in an association or union representing the interests
16 of the employees who would be eligible for the credit.
